                           </placeName>
                        </persName> and <persName nymRef="Cary">
                           <forename>Joan</forename> his wife</persName> a tenement, which he had of the gift of <persName nymRef="Berewyk">
                           <forename>Thomas</forename> son and heir of <persName>
                              <forename>Thomas</forename> of <surname>Berewyk</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, in <placeName key="place_107074">S. Mary the Greater</placeName>, between the messuage of <persName nymRef="Dene">
                           <forename>Agnes</forename> widow of <persName>
                              <forename>John</forename> atte <surname>Dene</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName> on the south, and that of <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename> 
                           <surname>Boty</surname>
                        </persName> on the north, reaching the highway on the west above the messuage of the said R. B. 
